<br>
Shadow Vortex is a good little buff if you are the main tank. It used to have a good agro, but doesnt at all anymore since the introduction of the recourse coponents for this kind of spell.<br>
<br>
Disease Coud used to the greatest agro generation spell in game. Its not anymore. This is nothing else than a 5hp dd + 1hp/tick dot. Pointless for damage. Some value for some very specific pulls, but thats about it. You shouldnt have this memed in your every day xp group, unless you are looking for a mana cheap spell to pull, but then you better not mind your mobs being non mezable due to the dot.<br>
<br>
So that leave us with Heat Blood, Heart Flutter and Cancel Magic and Resist Cold.<br>
<br>
Well, if you fight nuker, Resist Cold can be a good option.<br>
<br>
Cancel magic is cool if you hunt casters like mages, wizards, shamen, druids : to pull with cancel magic can get rid of their SoW, damage shield, haste or other buff. Makes your life easier when fighting them.<br>
<br>
Heat Blood is pretty weak damage over a fairly long period of time, not worth it.<br>
<br>
